00:16:46,573 --> 00:16:47,574
That's odd.

307
00:16:47,707 --> 00:16:49,576
Yeah.

308
00:16:49,709 --> 00:16:52,479
How does your father carry
someone else's dog tags

309
00:16:52,612 --> 00:16:55,115
