(SIGHS)

442
00:25:31,197 --> 00:25:32,965
Can you take your earbuds out,
please?

443
00:25:35,167 --> 00:25:36,167
(INHALES DEEPLY)

444
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:43,142
I don't think that I've
done anything wrong,

445
00:25:44,844 --> 00:25:47,580
