504
00:29:37,576 --> 00:29:38,577
(LAUGHS)

505
00:29:40,079 --> 00:29:41,080
(SIGHS)

506
00:29:42,882 --> 00:29:43,883
Yeah.

507
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:49,221
(CELLPHONE RINGING)

508
00:29:59,731 --> 00:30:00,766
Thank you for your call.

509
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:02,869
